    "summary": "Customer engagement,  e-CRM and loyalty professional. \nWinner of the DDMA Dialogue Marketeer of the Year Award 2015. \n\nExtensive marketing management experience in the airline, travel, telecommunications, retail and sports industry. Both in B2C and B2B markets. Hands-on experience in launching succesful omni-channel consumer and retail campaigns supporting brand and sales promotions in various markets. Developed and optimized loyalty programs for British Airways and Air Miles in The Netherlands. Managed CRM programs (acquisition, retention, up sell and win-back) in various sectors and markets. Experience with customer journey and customer satisfaction research programs that monitor the customer experience and relevant customer KPI\u2019s. Developed online and e-commerce channels in Europe, North America, Asia and Japan and improved commercial results by optimizing the customer online experience. Experience with implementation projects for and operating marketing of, marketing technologies such as: data warehouses, CRM marketing databases, marketing automation and multi-channel tools (e-commerce, mobile, e-care and CMS).\n\nEnthusiastic, motivated, and pragmatic team player with an interest for people, sports, technique, marketing, and communication. Driven by challenges, combining analytical approach with hands-on mentality. Eager to work in an environment where respect, transparency and creativity are vital for success. Team builder with a track record in building and developing strong marketing teams.\n\nExpertises: \n- Loyalty management\n- Database marketing\n- Omni-channel marketing\n- Retention programs\n- CRM programs\n- Online marketing\n- E-commerce\n- Real-time content personalisation\u2028\n- Advertising \n- Brand management",
